==Description==
The '''Crimson Shard''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]] first encountered in [[Sinnoh]].

==Details==
The Crimson Shard can be used, alongside [[Quest Points]] {{Questpoints}}, to purchase items at the [[Shard Trader|Shard Traders]].

==Mine Layout==
The Crimson Shard appears in the Underground as a 4x3 sized object: a 3x3 visible grid with an empty 1x3 row on the broken-edge side of the Shard image.<br><br>
[[File:CrimsonShardMine.png|100px]]

